      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'W,A,S,D to move

    ----------------------

    Space Bar to jump [double
    jump upgrade possible]

    C to crouch with morphball (upgrade needed)

    ----------------------

    Left
    Click to Fire Beam Shots (& morphbomb when upgrade aquired)

    Right Click
    to Fire Rockets (upgrade needed)

    R to restart level (you save when you get
    an upgrade or enter a level)


    If you get stuck spinning, just Left Click,
    it generally fixes it'
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
